Roll up summary 필드 타입 구하는 문제

NO.62 An app builder wants to streamline the user experience by reflecting summarized calculation
of specific fields on various objects.
Which three fields types should be used in roll-up summary fields to accomplish this?
Choose 3 answer
(A). Percent
(B). Checkbox
(C). Currency
(D). Date
(E). Time

퍼센트, 커런시, 데이트

NO.104 What type of field can be referenced by a Roll-up Summary field using SUM? Choose 3
answers
(A). Formula
(B). Currency
(C). Number
(D). Percent
(E). Date
Answer: B,C,D
여기서는 커런시, 넘버, 퍼센트 ( not date)

he types of fields you can calculate in a roll-up summary field depend on the type of calculation.
계산 타입에 따라,  roll-up summary filed에서 사용할 수 있는 타입이 결정 됨.

For example,
Number, currency, and percent fields are available when you select SUM as the roll-up type.
Number, currency, percent, date, and date/time fields are available when you select MIN or MAX as the roll-up type.

#### NO.161 Which two solutions prevent a formula field from being refrenced by a Roll-Up summary field
롤업 서머리 필드에 의해서 포뮬라가 참조되는것을 막기 위한 솔루션은 무엇인가요?
(A) A cross object workflow updating a field referenced by the formula field
(b) a cross object field reference in the formula field
(c) the CASE() function in the formula field
(d) the NOW()function in the formula field
답은 bd, d는 확실히 알겠는데 ( 롤업 요약 필드에 NOW 또는 TODAY와 같이 즉석에서 값을 파생하는 개체 간 필드 참조 또는 함수가 포함되어 있지 않으면 수식 필드 값을 계산할 수 있습니다)
a랑b는 잘 모르겠음

#### NO.274 Which statements are true regarding Roll-Up Summary fields? (select all thatapply)
(a) once created, you cannot change the detail object selected or delete any field referenced in your roll-up summary definition.
롤업 서머리가 한번 만들어지면, 디테일 오브젝트를 바꾸거나, 필드 참조를 바꿀 수 없다.
(b) because roll-up summary fields are not displayed on edit pages, you can use them in validation rules.
(c) validation errors can display when saving either the edtail or master record.
(d) advanced currency management has no affect on roll-up summary fields

